<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Verification Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #673AB7;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    .steps {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .step {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .step:before {
      content: "•";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #673AB7;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #673AB7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .note {
      background-color: #EDE7F6;
      border: 1px solid #D1C4E9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Account Verification Required</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{businessName}},</p>
      
      <p>To ensure the security of your account and enable full access to our payment processing features, we need to verify your business information.</p>
      
      <div class="steps">
        <h3>Required Documents:</h3>
        <div class="step">Business Registration Certificate</div>
        <div class="step">Government-issued ID of Business Owner</div>
        <div class="step">Proof of Business Address</div>
        <div class="step">Bank Account Statement</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="note">
        <strong>Note:</strong> The verification process typically takes 1-2 business days once all documents are submitted.
      </div>
      
      <a href="https://dashboard.pipaymentgateway.com/verification" class="button">
        Start Verification Process
      </a>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about the verification process, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2025 Pi Payment Gateway. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>